{"tid":959013,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"A7R3/A73用家有冇覺得手指尾好辛苦","createTime":"2018-12-28T09:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T13:36:59.000Z","uid":89757,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"fd023793c198a339048c0acd5ce0278acac4f3ed","tid":959013,"uid":89757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T09:14:53.000Z","msg":"我發覺真係差咁1cm隻手先揸得晒<br />\n搭支1635GM拎住行一粒鐘都開始頂唔住<br />\n<br />\n佢原廠個加長手柄又有啲柒同裝唔到快拆板<br />\n<br />\n所以我有兩個方案，<br />\n一係裝個L架 但唔知會唔會好唔方便同唔型<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZX9kZ0k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZX9kZ0k.png&h=79653e8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n二係裝個直倒，但好似真係大舊左啲同醜醜地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FYCra7m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFYCra7m.png&h=c16fc415&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴打有冇人用過分享下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea130d2183301202a18dc73b49644d761180a32c","tid":959013,"uid":89757,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T09:18:32.000Z","msg":"利申次次都係去瑩記買"},{"pid":"04e5623631fcf66b8dac861369ad425c217dd1e1","tid":959013,"uid":117044,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T09:20:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5550a24f898521122f2d70b1aab3628cef84c2a","tid":959013,"uid":226126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T09:37:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0f1511c32cc275cb185f9056392e5d4b35bd477","tid":959013,"uid":6848,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea130d2183301202a18dc73b49644d761180a32c","tid":959013,"uid":89757,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T09:18:32.000Z","msg":"利申次次都係去瑩記買"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T09:42:59.000Z","msg":"感覺優越？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41450f1d978fa9d0c99